In that case,

00:01:48.599 --> 00:01:50.959
let's fight our way out
of here together.

00:01:51.480 --> 00:01:53.159
Just like when we did
in the Nine Heavens.

00:01:53.879 --> 00:01:54.799
I don't believe

00:01:55.439 --> 00:01:56.480
there is no place for us

00:01:56.719 --> 00:01:58.319
in the Three Realms.

00:02:06.560 --> 00:02:07.040
Let's go.

00:02:09.199 --> 00:02:09.800
Chase them!

00:02:10.159 --> 00:02:11.819
- Stop!
- Stop!

00:02:11.819 --> 00:02:12.520
Let's get out!

00:02:42.599 --> 00:02:43.759
Why looking at me like that?

00:02:48.800 --> 00:02:50.000
You once said

00:02:51.080 --> 00:02:52.000
you loved me.

00:02:53.879 --> 00:02:54.960
Was that in my past life?

00:02:57.719 --> 00:02:58.520
How did you know?

00:03:10.879 --> 00:03:12.000
You said before,

00:03:12.960 --> 00:03:14.199
300 years ago,

00:03:15.280 --> 00:03:17.840
your hope was shattered.

00:03:19.240 --> 00:03:20.159
You once

00:03:22.080 --> 00:03:23.360
killed me, right?

00:03:31.560 --> 00:03:32.120
I wanted

00:03:33.479 --> 00:03:34.719
to follow you in death.

00:03:35.680 --> 00:03:38.400
The Immortal Lord told me
you'd reappear after 300 years later.

00:03:38.879 --> 00:03:39.639
I never expected

00:03:41.639 --> 00:03:43.479
the Night Deity would
revive within you too.

00:03:47.199 --> 00:03:48.520
Can't we

00:03:49.759 --> 00:03:51.120
change our fates?

00:03:59.639 --> 00:04:00.840
300 years without you

00:04:03.240 --> 00:04:04.919
was far too long.

00:04:07.080 --> 00:04:10.944
Yet I don't want to kill you again
after 300 years.

00:04:13.000 --> 00:04:13.599
Chuli.

00:04:15.120 --> 00:04:16.040
I've decided

00:04:17.160 --> 00:04:18.519
to die with you.

00:04:20.000 --> 00:04:21.680
Then we'll never be apart again.

00:04:22.680 --> 00:04:23.879
No, Chen.

00:04:24.680 --> 00:04:25.720
You must live well.

00:04:27.600 --> 00:04:28.319
Do you know?

00:04:30.920 --> 00:04:32.319
If every 300 years,

00:04:33.160 --> 00:04:34.680
I'm meant to be killed by someone,

00:04:36.879 --> 00:04:38.079
and then I'd rather it is you.

00:04:38.199 --> 00:04:38.759
Chuli.

00:04:39.600 --> 00:04:41.279
When I revive after 300 years,

00:04:41.920 --> 00:04:42.839
and you're gone,

00:04:43.959 --> 00:04:44.879
what should I do?

00:04:45.800 --> 00:04:47.000
Where would I go look for you?

00:04:50.639 --> 00:04:52.040
You have to live well,

00:04:53.279 --> 00:04:54.560
so we can meet again.

00:04:55.199 --> 00:04:55.680
No.

00:05:00.120 --> 00:05:01.040
Swear to me

00:05:01.480 --> 00:05:02.680
that you'll live well

00:05:03.199 --> 00:05:04.899
and never abandon your life for me.

00:05:05.800 --> 00:05:06.519
Why?

00:05:09.959 --> 00:05:11.319
That's too cruel to me.

00:05:13.759 --> 00:05:15.160
This is my wish.

00:05:15.920 --> 00:05:17.560
Can't you grant me even this?

00:05:27.879 --> 00:05:28.360
Alright.

00:05:29.000 --> 00:05:29.720
I promise.

00:05:32.160 --> 00:05:32.720
Good.

00:05:33.600 --> 00:05:34.959
If you break this,

00:05:35.720 --> 00:05:36.920
I will be reduced to ashes

00:05:37.160 --> 00:05:38.319
and never reincarnate.

00:05:39.920 --> 00:05:40.480
Chuli.

00:05:41.480 --> 00:05:42.839
Don't do this to me.

00:05:44.720 --> 00:05:46.920
I'm selfish and domineering.

00:05:47.759 --> 00:05:49.439
I just want you to live well.

00:05:50.319 --> 00:05:53.120
That way every time I revive,

00:05:53.879 --> 00:05:55.000
I can meet you again.

00:06:08.720 --> 00:06:09.240
Okay.

00:06:17.399 --> 00:06:18.279
In that case,

00:06:20.639 --> 00:06:22.120
go reclaim the Divine Sword.

00:06:26.432 --> 00:06:29.344
