00:07:03.439 --> 00:07:04.079
What's wrong?

00:07:04.928 --> 00:07:05.728
What's on your mind?

00:07:08.360 --> 00:07:08.959
Nothing.

00:07:10.360 --> 00:07:11.360
I was just thinking

00:07:12.639 --> 00:07:15.680
if possible, I'd like to die
in the sea of flowers.

00:07:16.319 --> 00:07:17.079
Don't say that!

00:07:19.439 --> 00:07:20.800
I won't let you die.

00:07:21.560 --> 00:07:22.920
I mean, if...

00:07:23.120 --> 00:07:23.959
No way!

00:07:29.360 --> 00:07:30.079
Pity

00:07:32.199 --> 00:07:33.680
that my blood makes flowers wither.

00:07:48.120 --> 00:07:48.800
Pretty?

00:08:09.800 --> 00:08:10.240
Chuli.

00:08:11.399 --> 00:08:11.839
Chuli.

00:08:13.160 --> 00:08:13.660
How are you?

00:08:14.495 --> 00:08:15.040
How are you?

00:08:15.519 --> 00:08:16.100
Answer me.

00:08:16.360 --> 00:08:16.800
Answer me.

00:08:17.720 --> 00:08:18.360
I'm here.

00:08:20.040 --> 00:08:20.560
I'm here.

00:08:20.720 --> 00:08:21.399
Kill me.

00:08:22.120 --> 00:08:22.720
Please.

00:08:23.560 --> 00:08:24.439
I won't kill you.

00:08:27.000 --> 00:08:28.040
Please.

00:08:29.680 --> 00:08:30.519
Kill me.

00:08:31.319 --> 00:08:33.240
I don't want to be like this anymore.

00:08:34.200 --> 00:08:34.960
Wake up.

00:08:35.559 --> 00:08:36.159
Chuli.

00:10:24.320 --> 00:10:25.000
It seems

00:10:26.679 --> 00:10:28.120
you still remember our promise.

00:10:31.480 --> 00:10:32.299
I remember.

00:10:33.440 --> 00:10:34.240
Take up your sword

00:10:36.600 --> 00:10:37.480
and point it at me.

00:10:40.600 --> 00:10:42.080
You're the War God of Nine Heavens.

00:10:44.039 --> 00:10:44.879
Only in this way

00:10:46.784 --> 00:10:49.960
will Night Deity stop controlling me
and endangering the Three Realms.

00:11:10.200 --> 00:11:11.000
Do it now.

00:11:13.200 --> 00:11:14.360
While I'm still myself.

00:11:16.519 --> 00:11:17.919
I want to be

00:11:18.600 --> 00:11:20.399
with you at my last moment.

00:11:55.399 --> 00:11:55.879
Chuli.

00:11:55.879 --> 00:11:59.279
As expected, I am better.

