How did you find me?

00:15:17.600 --> 00:15:18.039
Sir.

00:15:18.240 --> 00:15:19.519
Don't reject me yet.

00:15:20.080 --> 00:15:22.480
Everyone knows
Lord Yongzhao Bai Lingjia.

00:15:23.080 --> 00:15:24.399
She requests to meet you,

00:15:24.480 --> 00:15:25.799
must be for crucial matters.

00:15:26.080 --> 00:15:27.679
Please come with us.

00:15:28.840 --> 00:15:29.919
Lord Yongzhao?

00:15:31.199 --> 00:15:32.639
Does Wanfeng have someone like that?

00:15:33.720 --> 00:15:34.519
Wanfeng Kingdom?

00:15:37.120 --> 00:15:39.919
It perished 200 years ago.

00:15:44.399 --> 00:15:45.559
It perished?

00:15:49.500 --> 00:15:50.139
Leave.

00:15:51.940 --> 00:15:53.100
I won't leave here.

00:15:54.139 --> 00:15:55.419
Don't be that arrogant.

00:15:55.419 --> 00:15:55.860
Stop!

00:15:57.220 --> 00:15:57.700
Sir.

00:15:58.460 --> 00:16:00.820
This matter isn't yours to refuse.

00:16:01.419 --> 00:16:02.460
This is the Lord's decree.

00:16:02.659 --> 00:16:04.580
You're now summoned to the capital.

00:16:05.100 --> 00:16:06.259
Defiance means death.

00:16:13.659 --> 00:16:15.879
(It's the same pattern as
on that jade pendant.)

00:16:17.360 --> 00:16:18.320
(Could it be her?)

00:16:23.879 --> 00:16:24.279
Fine.

00:16:25.899 --> 00:16:26.820
I'll go with you.

00:16:38.159 --> 00:16:38.639
Lord.

00:16:38.759 --> 00:16:40.129
Master of Snowfall Valley is here.

00:16:41.039 --> 00:16:41.519
Good.

00:16:42.679 --> 00:16:44.519
General Nian, you never disappoint me.

00:16:45.120 --> 00:16:45.659
Reward.

00:16:46.240 --> 00:16:46.960
Thank you, Lord.

00:17:05.519 --> 00:17:06.640
(I've finally seen you.)

00:17:10.480 --> 00:17:11.720
I've long heard your fame.

00:17:12.519 --> 00:17:13.759
Though you've secluded,

00:17:14.480 --> 00:17:16.480
still perceived the big picture.

00:17:18.119 --> 00:17:20.279
If you can assist me,

00:17:21.400 --> 00:17:22.839
I can unite the six cities.

00:17:24.880 --> 00:17:25.920
I'm flattered.

00:17:27.200 --> 00:17:28.519
I've long withdrawn

00:17:28.839 --> 00:17:29.720
from the worldly ties.

00:17:30.599 --> 00:17:32.000
I might not be able to assist you.

00:17:32.839 --> 00:17:34.279
Coming with General Nian today

00:17:35.920 --> 00:17:38.319
was solely to tell you this myself.

00:17:38.839 --> 00:17:39.640
Nothing more.

00:17:43.799 --> 00:17:45.160
Don't refuse yet.

00:17:46.000 --> 00:17:49.319
Hear my offer.

00:17:51.599 --> 00:17:52.960
If you assist me,

00:17:54.799 --> 00:17:55.880
henceforth,

00:17:56.759 --> 00:17:58.160
you'll be National Preceptor,

00:17:58.440 --> 00:18:00.119
who only serves me.

00:18:00.880 --> 00:18:02.599
- What?
- How could he be?

00:18:04.400 --> 00:18:06.200
When I unite the six cities,

00:18:07.359 --> 00:18:09.200
we'll share the realm.

00:18:09.519 --> 00:18:10.759
It's tempting indeed,

00:18:11.920 --> 00:18:13.359
but not what I want.

00:18:14.519 --> 00:18:17.160
What do you want?

00:18:19.960 --> 00:18:20.839
You can't offer

00:18:22.279 --> 00:18:23.599
what I want.

00:18:31.759 --> 00:18:32.559
Leave us.

00:18:33.799 --> 00:18:36.279
I need to speak privately with him.

00:18:37.160 --> 00:18:39.240
- Yes, Lord.
- Yes, Lord.

00:18:56.440 --> 00:18:57.079
Sir.

00:18:58.559 --> 00:18:59.759
Have we met before?

00:19:06.720 --> 00:19:07.880
Why do you ask this?

00:19:11.759 --> 00:19:13.400
Because in your eyes,

00:19:14.759 --> 00:19:16.359
there's something different.

00:19:19.359 --> 00:19:20.000
But I

00:19:21.759 --> 00:19:22.839
don't understand why.

00:19:23.640 --> 00:19:24.720
You misunderstand.

00:19:25.839 --> 00:19:26.960
To me,

00:19:27.880 --> 00:19:30.480
you are nothing different from others.

00:19:36.480 --> 00:19:37.599
I see.

00:19:46.200 --> 00:19:47.000
Lord.

00:19:47.359 --> 00:19:48.839
You are finally here.

00:19:50.279 --> 00:19:50.839
Lord.

00:19:50.839 --> 00:19:52.200
It has been a while.

00:19:52.480 --> 00:19:54.599
I miss you every single day.

00:19:54.839 --> 00:19:55.799
So do we.

00:19:55.799 --> 00:19:56.559
Exactly.

00:19:56.559 --> 00:19:57.960
My duties kept me occupied.

00:19:59.480 --> 00:20:01.400
That's why I summoned you here.

00:20:05.079 --> 00:20:06.119
Who is he?

00:20:07.000 --> 00:20:07.680
He is

00:20:08.599 --> 00:20:10.759
a recluse I want to recruit
from seclusion.

00:20:11.960 --> 00:20:13.200
Show him proper respect.

00:20:13.799 --> 00:20:15.000
- Yes.
- Yes.

00:20:15.240 --> 00:20:16.240
I summoned you

00:20:17.039 --> 00:20:18.599
to see

00:20:19.079 --> 00:20:20.400
if the way he looks at me

00:20:21.319 --> 00:20:23.200
is like yours.

00:20:24.720 --> 00:20:27.480
Yet he denied it

00:20:28.079 --> 00:20:31.000
and claimed the way he looks at me
is nothing special.

00:20:33.400 --> 00:20:34.400
In my opinion,

00:20:34.920 --> 00:20:37.119
the way he looks at you

00:20:37.720 --> 00:20:39.359
is way more intense than ours.

00:20:39.519 --> 00:20:40.440
Exactly.

00:20:41.160 --> 00:20:43.119
We admire you with devotion,

00:20:43.440 --> 00:20:44.359
but he

00:20:45.720 --> 00:20:47.680
harbors soul-crushing anguish

00:20:48.640 --> 00:20:50.200
and obsession.

00:20:50.480 --> 00:20:53.000
His eyes reveal
a desire of possessiveness

00:20:53.200 --> 00:20:55.799
to you exclusively.

00:20:55.880 --> 00:20:58.920
As if you belong solely to him.

00:20:59.319 --> 00:21:00.319
More than that.

00:21:00.680 --> 00:21:02.680
There's madness and repression.

00:21:04.980 --> 00:21:05.579
Lord.

00:21:06.019 --> 00:21:07.539
Ignore him. Here.

00:21:19.039 --> 00:21:19.519
Get lost!

00:21:27.440 --> 00:21:28.640
You don't seem

00:21:29.720 --> 00:21:32.160
to have long withdrawn
from the worldly ties

00:21:32.640 --> 00:21:33.799
as you claimed.

00:21:38.640 --> 00:21:40.759
Since you drove away my playthings,

00:21:42.319 --> 00:21:43.160
then you'll

00:21:44.200 --> 00:21:45.240
come entertain me.

00:22:01.440 --> 00:22:04.160
♪The candle shines my troubled heart♪

00:22:04.160 --> 00:22:06.657
♪Swaying through restless nights♪

00:22:07.520 --> 00:22:09.344
♪Flute melodies linger tenderly♪

